high_descs: Turn right and walk to the table in front of you and take a half step to your right.
Pick up the pen to the left of the book.
Turn right and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the other wall then turn right to face a night stand.
Put the pen to the left of the mug on the night stand.
Go back to where you got the first pen but take a step right from that spot so you are looking at the other side of the table.
Pick up the pen that's above the mug.
Go back to where you put the first pen.
Stand this pen up so it's leaning against the alarm clock.
anns.task_desc: Put two pens on the night stand.

Grab the pen from the desk

Place the pen on top of the night stand
Walk over back to the desk
Grab the pen from the desk
Walk back to the night stand
Place the pen on top of the night stand

high_descs: Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and walk up to the table.
Pick up the pen that is closest to the laptop on the table.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk over to the small nightstand.
Place the pen on the nigthstand between the mug and the alarm clock.
Walk over to the bed, then turn right and head back to the table with the laptop on it.
Pick up the pen that is behind the black mug from the table.
Turn right and head over to the nightstand next to the bed.
Place the pen point down on the nightstand in between the alarm clock and the mug.
